                    "description": "\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDataset Card for \"ultrafeedback_binarized_cleaned\"\n\t\n\nUpdate 1/12/2023: I've removed examples identified as faulty by Argilla - see their awesome work for more details.\nThis is a version of the UltraFeedback binarized dataset but with TruthfulQA prompts removed and source annotations added (so you can filter out samples from different sources yourself if you want!).\nPlease see the binarized dataset card for more information, or the original UltraFeedback dataset card.\n",
